captions.text:
"Title in the Middle",
everybody plays.

What's the deal with
"Title in the Middle"?

Our improv musician Daniel
Tauszig will play a theme song,

and this theme will inspire
our players to do a scene.

I ring the bell and
the scene freezes.

I'll get one of the sentences
you wrote outside and it will

be the scene title, and they'll
have to make this title match

with the scene they
have already started.

We'll do a number of
scenes and they all start

with a theme song from
Daniel Tauszig, please.
Who's there?
Oh, it's a dog.
I don't have a dog!

Okay, after the bell,
no one else can join the scene.
The title for this scene is...

'You will want me,
whether you want it or not'

I can't believe this...
Who's there? Who's there?
I don't have a dog!
Hi! It's me, Roberto!

- What are you doing here?
- We met each other 45 years ago.

And you left me waiting. I still have
the flower I was going to give you!

Look, son,
I got married, I had kids...

And you will want me,
whether you want it or not!
How cute...
How cute!
Daniel Tauszig, next theme!

After the bell,
no one else can join...
And the title for the scene is...
'I plant to eat'

They don't make public
libraries like they used to!
Motherfuckers!

You're not supposed
to be talking in english!

Oh, my book? 'I Plant to Eat'.
It's a great book...

Daniel Tauszig,
next theme, please.

If you're not coming,
I'll go alone, baby!

- Oh, I don't know...
- Come with me, baby!
His car has electric windows...
But my car has my heart in it!

And the title for the scene is:
'Dirty floor, dirty floor, dirty floor'.
Hey, baby!
I have money!
Come!
All I can offer you is my heart!
Oh, how cute!

- Do you have another helmet?
- I do!
Wait. I'll just grab a book.

'Dirty Floor, Dirty Floor,
Dirty Floor'

The game is a lot easier
if we can justify it like this!

- So, the game works like this...
- One: He wasn't even in a library.

Two: He can't speak right,
he said 'dirry floor, dirry floor'!

CIA. BARBIXAS DE HUMOR
presented

IMPROVÁVEL
Probably a good show.
Electric fan, so good.

- Change!
- This death should just die!
